1
00:00:01,233 --> 00:00:03,234
[SPEAKER_08]: Welcome everyone to our November meeting.

2
00:00:04,494 --> 00:00:07,195
[SPEAKER_08]: I want to just get started right away because we have a big agenda.

3
00:00:08,055 --> 00:00:13,737
