194
00:19:50,771 --> 00:19:53,753
[SPEAKER_04]: Is there any, and maybe this is for people at the Collins Center,

195
00:19:54,157 --> 00:20:06,741
[SPEAKER_04]: Do we have any data or any information on how people feel in different cities or towns who have individual ward counselors or just citywide counselors?

196
00:20:06,781 --> 00:20:13,683
[SPEAKER_04]: Do they feel any more represented if they have a ward counselor as opposed to at large counselors?

197
00:20:15,523 --> 00:20:16,404
[SPEAKER_12]: I'd have to look into that.

198
00:20:16,424 --> 00:20:18,664
