[SPEAKER_04]: Yeah, I guess because a concern of mine is, or something I think about is, I'm not even really sure that a lot of the residents are even aware of or know that they have a ward councillor or a large councillor.

206
00:21:09,832 --> 00:21:14,116
[SPEAKER_04]: I'm not sure they're even in tune with what the represents

207
00:21:14,943 --> 00:21:18,205
