00:27:45,509 --> 00:28:06,459
[SPEAKER_16]: I'm in favor of what representation, but I want to know, especially when we have to present to the city council, the reasons why we took this path, you know, that we have, you know, some solid evidence to back it up, or if not, they're just going to dismiss our findings.

295
