01:21:51,445 --> 01:22:04,572
[SPEAKER_01]: not only report on the status of the current year, but where the mayor foresees, not a commitment per se, as I recall, but foresees the next budget headed.

923
01:22:06,253 --> 01:22:07,613
[SPEAKER_01]: But that's not by charter.

924
01:22:07,873 --> 01:22:16,598
[SPEAKER_01]: That's, again, the whole issue of the potential conflict with state statute, but I believe that's by ordinance.

