01:22:49,919 --> 01:22:57,362
[SPEAKER_10]: Can you modify the state law or is that what we have to work with, I guess?

930
01:22:57,402 --> 01:23:05,824
[SPEAKER_12]: Sorry, I was just reading through the state statute.

931
01:23:06,544 --> 01:23:12,486
[SPEAKER_12]: My understanding is that you can put, as the mayor has,

932
01:23:19,637 --> 01:23:23,218
[SPEAKER_12]: is the mayor has the state statute.

933
01:23:23,238 --> 01:23:26,760
[SPEAKER_12]: Basically, you can't overwrite the state statute.

934
01:23:27,980 --> 01:23:28,280
[SPEAKER_10]: Okay.

935
01:23:30,561 --> 01:23:34,262
[SPEAKER_10]: Is that something you could share with us so we know what the timeline is in that?

936
01:23:36,863 --> 01:23:37,603
[SPEAKER_10]: That would be helpful.

