938
01:23:48,437 --> 01:24:11,472
[SPEAKER_02]: in several city charters that the mayor presents some picture of the city's revenue forecast fairly early in the year, like March or April, so that people know what your revenues are expected to be and what some of your fixed costs are, and that provides some foundation for the budget deliberations going forward.

939
01:24:12,473 --> 01:24:16,175
[SPEAKER_02]: We've also had communities that have put financial forecasts

940
01:24:16,920 --> 01:24:23,562
[SPEAKER_02]: in their charter, requiring that a financial forecast be provided of three to five years.

941
01:24:23,582 --> 01:24:29,583
[SPEAKER_02]: So the communities will, once again, have an idea of what their picture looks like going forward.

942
01:24:32,744 --> 01:24:35,265
[SPEAKER_10]: I think things like that would be helpful.

943
01:24:35,365 --> 01:24:43,327
